{"id": "1217899871764349009", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "848454386598412318", "author_name": "ruko9999", "author_bot": false, "content": "6章守密自己一個人就完成墨菲的喚醒體構成我就覺得有點恐怖了（X\n至於意識淺遊的部份只能說\n我們入侵的都是喚醒體的夢\n多少都會被高位存在發現（X\n至少我們已經被發現好幾次了", "timestamp": "2024-03-14T18:19:16.914000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["426913095701495811"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1217878893390725201", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1217905392064004137", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "1207347087369568268", "author_name": "jpzr2323", "author_bot": false, "content": "我觉得按照克系的理解，应该是我（守密人）一直在做梦，只不过有时候睡的比较深（人工秘境&&意识潜游），有时候比较浅（处于现实），在第六章受伤比较严重的时候，甚至能听到吹笛声（快被吵醒了），醒了的话的话就掀桌子了", "timestamp": "2024-03-14T18:41:13.056000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["848454386598412318"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1217899871764349009", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1217905976644997311", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 19, "author_id": "426913095701495811", "author_name": "mob1065", "author_bot": false, "content": "守密人就是章魚本人嗎", "timestamp": "2024-03-14T18:43:32.431000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1207347087369568268"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1217905392064004137", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
